00:48:51.620 --> 00:48:56.290
Rather, it is an arm's
length sales-based industry.

00:48:56.290 --> 00:48:59.140
The great challenge for
society and for the industry

00:48:59.140 --> 00:49:05.390
itself is to transform
itself into a profession.

00:49:05.390 --> 00:49:07.140
In light of the
conflicts of interest

00:49:07.140 --> 00:49:09.710
and asymmetries of
information that

00:49:09.710 --> 00:49:12.180
are inherent in investing
and money management,

00:49:12.180 --> 00:49:14.640
I would say this is
a matter of urgency

00:49:14.640 --> 00:49:16.520
