duty at the present time

00:50:03.025 --> 00:50:04.800
at law, which is crazy.

00:50:04.800 --> 00:50:06.580
It's what I just
described as a baby step.

00:50:09.210 --> 00:50:12.500
And in light of that, it
falls to the individual

00:50:12.500 --> 00:50:16.260
to take action for herself.

00:50:16.260 --> 00:50:18.300
So here's the prescription.

00:50:18.300 --> 00:50:20.310
Here's what I think
you need to do.

00:50:20.310 --> 00:50:23.450
I think you need to look for
individuals and companies

00:50:23.450 --> 00:50:26.570
to work with who exhibit
these professional qualities

00:50:26.570 --> 00:50:30.580
that I've talked about,
and who understand

00:50:30.580 --> 00:50:36.050
their responsibilities in
safeguarding and care-taking

00:50:36.050 --> 00:50:37.840
of their clients in their work.

00:50:40.550 --> 00:50:44.430
In this quest, here's
what you need to do.

00:50:44.430 --> 00:50:46.860
You need to do a
lot of preparation.

00:50:46.860 --> 00:50:49.240
You need to ask a tremendous
amount of questions.

00:50:49.240 --> 00:50:52.550
You need to do your homework
and know the subject area.

00:50:52.550 --> 00:50:54.120
Do your research.

00:50:54.120 --> 00:50:55.850
Be skeptical.

00:50:55.850 --> 00:50:56.795
Own your own power.

00:50:56.795 --> 00:51:00.380
This is very important
because a lot of us

00:51:00.380 --> 00:51:04.880
mistake financial people for the
people who tell us what to do

00:51:04.880 --> 00:51:08.300
and we just accept, like
doctors and lawyers and clergy.

00:51:08.300 --> 00:51:09.540
That's a mistake.

00:51:09.540 --> 00:51:11.610
You are the one in
the power position.

00:51:11.610 --> 00:51:14.800
In fact, to go back
to a concept mentioned

00:51:14.800 --> 00:51:17.430
