00:51:27.850 --> 00:51:29.530
You've got a lot of choices.

00:51:29.530 --> 00:51:31.820
That means you have the power.

00:51:31.820 --> 00:51:35.020
Own that power.

00:51:35.020 --> 00:51:37.600
