an awful lot of people

00:57:38.210 --> 00:57:40.418
call themselves financial
advisors when what they are

00:57:40.418 --> 00:57:41.710
is investment advisers.

00:57:41.710 --> 00:57:45.450
That's even how they're
regulated, just by investments.

00:57:45.450 --> 00:57:48.005
Robo may be able to do a
reasonably good job of choosing

00:57:48.005 --> 00:57:50.080
an investment portfolio for you.

00:57:50.080 --> 00:57:52.670
There's a whole lot more
to your financial life,

00:57:52.670 --> 00:57:55.600
and I don't know that Robo
can do anything with it.

00:57:55.600 --> 00:57:58.580
So the answer is, perhaps
just for investments,

00:57:58.580 --> 00:58:01.780
maybe it's-- I don't have a
full opinion, it's just coming.

00:58:01.780 --> 00:58:04.992
For a full guidance with
